sections.heading: Overview
content:
Sean Ceaser, ND, is an adjunct clinical professor of research in diabetes
and homeopathy at the Natural Health Sciences Research Clinic in Lake Oswego,
Ore. and a Type I diabetic. He is a graduate of the National College of
Naturopathic Medicine in Portland, Ore., one of four accredited naturopathic
colleges in the United States.
